(30, 8, '\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\n\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nThe Amazon points given for this item are granted to be combined and given to each individual item. Please check your order confirmation screen for the exact number of points.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (left): Easy Installation: No construction required, anyone can install it with one touch. Even those who don\'t like construction can easily install this product so you can enjoy a comfortable and smart life. The main body is hidden behind the curtain, making it easy to blend in with your home decor.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (left): [Various operations] Touch&amp;Go, app operation. When you pull the curtain lightly with your hand, it detects movement quickly, and automatically opens and closes the curtain in the direction you want to move. In addition, you can operate and check the opening and closing from the app anytime, anywhere. (*When linked with the hub series, there is no control distance limit. You can also operate the dedicated remote button (sold separately).\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (left): [Automatically opens and closes when it senses sunlight] Built-in light sensor that automatically opens and closes when it senses sunlight. It will not be affected by the sound of the operation and will make you feel refreshed. It helps to improve your sleep rhythm and help you live a healthy lifestyle. Of course, you can also set the timer.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (left): [More convenient when connected with the smart speaker] When used with the SwitchBot hub series, you can operate the SwitchBot curtain with the voice control of the smart speaker. Compatible with Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, Siri Shortcuts, IFTTT, LINE Clova (Beta). Smart and efficient on busy mornings.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (Right): Easy to install: Set up with 3 simple tapes by installing the dedicated SwitchBot app. Attach it to your fridge or wall with the included magnetic sheet. A smart thermometer/hygrometer that can be used anywhere.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nProduct (Right): (High Precision Swiss Sensor) Equipped with a Swiss temperature and humidity sensor that allows for a reliable temperature and humidity measurement with greater accuracy and control.\n\n</span></li>\n\n</ul>\n<!--  Loading EDP related metadata -->\n\n\n\n\n<span class=\"edp-feature-declaration\" data-edp-feature-name=\"featurebullets\" data-edp-asin=\"B08NXXCDNM\" data-data-hash=\"1289545411\" data-defects=\"[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-mismatch-info&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Different from product&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-missing-information&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Missing information&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-unessential-info&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Unimportant information&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-other-productinfo-issue&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Other&quot;}]\" data-metadata=\"CATALOG\" data-feature-container-id=\"\" data-custom-event-handler=\"\" data-display-name=\"Bullet Points\" data-edit-data-state=\"featureBulletsEDPEditData\" data-position=\"\" data-resolver=\"CQResolver\"></span>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"a-row a-expander-container a-expander-inline-container\">\n<div aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-extend-content\" style=\"display:none\">\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Product (Right): (You can check historical data) The thermometer/hygrometer has been stored via Bluetooth. When used with a hub, a thermometer/hygrometer can store all data recordings from paired to previous versions.</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Product (Right): [Alarm Included] With the hub